FacetGrid¶

  • 想把 数据集 很多子集 进行展示的时候
  • 首先，要把 展示区域 勾勒出来
  • 再通过 map 函数,去把实际的图构造出来
In [3]:
g = sns.FacetGrid(tips, col="time")
In [4]:
g = sns.FacetGrid(tips, col="time")
g.map(plt.hist, "tip")
In [14]:
g = sns.FacetGrid(tips, col="sex", hue="smoker")
g.map(plt.scatter, "total_bill", "tip", alpha=.7)
g.add_legend()

In [18]:
# margin_titles=True指定 row 显示在每行上
g = sns.FacetGrid(tips, row="smoker", col="time", margin_titles=True)
# fit_reg=True指定回归的线是否画出
g.map(sns.regplot, "size", "total_bill", color=".1", fit_reg=True, x_jitter=.1);

from pandas import Categorical
ordered_days = tips.day.value_counts().index
print (ordered_days)

ordered_days = Categorical(['Thur', 'Fri', 'Sat', 'Sun'])

# row_order用指定为指定数据(用pandas)
g = sns.FacetGrid(tips, row="day", row_order=ordered_days,
                  size=1.7, aspect=4,)
g.map(sns.boxplot, "total_bill")

In [36]:
# pal在下面的palette指定调色板，用字典的形式；多个类别写多个颜色；
pal = dict(Lunch="seagreen", Dinner="gray")
g = sns.FacetGrid(tips, hue="time", palette=pal, size=5)
g.map(plt.scatter, "total_bill", "tip", s=50, alpha=.7, linewidth=.5, edgecolor="white")
g.add_legend();

In [52]:
with sns.axes_style("white"):
    g = sns.FacetGrid(tips, row="sex", col="smoker", margin_titles=True, size=2.5)
g.map(plt.scatter, "total_bill", "tip", color="#334488", edgecolor="white", lw=0.5, alpha=0.9)
# 设分别置 x 轴 和  y 轴
g.set_axis_labels("Total bill (US Dollars)", "Tip")
# 设置轴的取值范围
g.set(xticks=[10, 30, 50], yticks=[2, 6, 10])
# 设置关于子图与子图之间的间隔比值
g.fig.subplots_adjust(wspace=.02, hspace=.02)
# 整个图的偏移
#g.fig.subplots_adjust(left  = 0.125,right = 0.5,bottom = 0.1,top = 0.9, wspace=.02, hspace=.02)
